# D{{N}} — Failure / Fallback Decision Tree: {{POLICY_TITLE}}

**Audience:** Engineer + Operations (incident response and on-call playbook).
**When to look at this:** When `{{TRIGGER_EVENT}}` fires — to know which path the system takes, what the user sees, and which terminal state is acceptable.
**Prose gap closed:** ADR `{{ADR_REF}}` describes the policy in prose; this diagram shows the **branching logic** so on-call engineers can scan it under pressure.

