## What happens when {{TRIGGER_EVENT}} fires

> **Trigger:** {{TRIGGER_DESCRIPTION}}
> **Governed by:** [`{{ADR_REF}}`](../7-adr/{{ADR_REF}})

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    ROOT(["<b>{{TRIGGER_EVENT}}</b>"]):::trigger

    {{#BRANCHES}}
    {{id}}{"<b>{{condition}}</b><br/>{{label}}"}
    {{/BRANCHES}}

    {{#TERMINAL_OUTCOMES}}
    {{id}}["{{label}}"]:::{{terminal_class}}
    {{/TERMINAL_OUTCOMES}}

    %% Edges (parent → child) — the tree topology
    {{#EDGES}}
    {{from_id}} -->|"{{label}}"| {{to_id}}
    {{/EDGES}}

    classDef trigger fill:#fff7d6,stroke:#b78a00,stroke-width:2px,color:#222
    classDef happy fill:#d6f5d6,stroke:#2e8b2e,color:#222
    classDef degraded fill:#ffe4b5,stroke:#c8740a,color:#222
    classDef failed fill:#ffd6d6,stroke:#c23838,color:#222
```

