## Legend

| Symbol | Meaning |
|--------|---------|
| Yellow rounded rectangle | Trigger event (root of the tree) |
| Diamond | Decision node — runtime condition |
| 🟢 Green leaf | Happy terminal outcome |
| 🟧 Amber leaf | Degraded terminal outcome (acceptable) |
| 🟥 Red leaf | Failed terminal outcome (acceptable per ADR) |
| Edge label | The condition that selects this branch (e.g. `yes`, `no`, `>3 retries`) |

